# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @platform/ai-engine — provider configuration.
#
# Two layers of configuration:
#
#   1. Vendor API keys                  (one per provider that's authorised)
#   2. Provider chains per capability   (controls primary + fallback order)
#
# All env vars are read at registry-resolution time, NOT at module-load time.
# This means an unset key produces a degraded adapter that fails healthCheck()
# gracefully — never a hard crash at process start. Studio + workers can
# import @platform/ai-engine even with zero keys configured; only the
# capability-specific call paths surface the missing credentials.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Vendor API keys ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Anthropic — text + vision primary (Claude 3.5 Sonnet for reasoning + Arabic
# copywriting, Claude 3.5 Haiku for cheap health pings).
# https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# OpenAI — text + vision fallback, embeddings primary.
# https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# fal.ai — image generation (Flux Pro 1.1 for photo, Recraft v3 for Arabic
# in-image text).
# https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
FAL_KEY=

# Firecrawl — supplier-URL scraping (PLATFORM.md §11 stage 02).
# https://www.firecrawl.dev/app/api-keys
FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=


# ── Provider chains (per capability) ────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Comma-separated chain: "anthropic,openai" means Anthropic primary,
# OpenAI fallback. The registry parses this string, instantiates each
# adapter in order, and returns { primary, fallbacks[] } for the
# capability.
#
# Leaving a variable unset uses the default chain documented next to it.
# Setting it overrides — including with a single-item chain (no fallback).

# Default: anthropic,openai
STUDIO_TEXT_PROVIDERS=

# Default: anthropic,openai
STUDIO_VISION_PROVIDERS=

# Default: fal
STUDIO_IMAGE_PROVIDERS=

# Default: firecrawl
STUDIO_SCRAPER_PROVIDERS=

# Default: openai
STUDIO_EMBED_PROVIDERS=
